text: Spotted Joe-pye weed (Eutrochium maculatum) is a species of plant. It belongs in the family Asteraceae. It is found in North America. Its height ranges from 60 to 200 cm. (24 to 79 in.). ==Other websites== *Eutrochium maculatum at Flora of North America *Eutrochium maculatum at Germplasm Resources Information Network Category:Asteraceae
title: Eutrochium maculatum
